headline: 3 Reasons We Love Rollins (ROL)
summary: Over the past six months, Rollins has been a great trade, beating the S&P 500 by 11%. Its stock price has climbed to $57.64, representing a healthy 16.4% increase. This run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
